title: Minister for Defence Materiel and Science – Queenslanders follow Anzac tradition (Department of Defence - ...
text: ( Source : Department of Defence - Australian Government ) Minister for Defence Materiel and Science , the Hon Mal Brough MP, today met 29 of Queensland 's newest Army recruits at their Public Enlistment Ceremony at Brisbane's ANZAC Square .
